<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Knowledge on Jabberwocky</title><link>https://avaritiachaos.github.io/tags/knowledge/</link><description>Recent content in Knowledge on Jabberwocky</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><copyright>Example Person</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Apr 2023 18:03:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://avaritiachaos.github.io/tags/knowledge/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>VS Code——Live Server插件</title><link>https://avaritiachaos.github.io/p/vs-codelive-server%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Sat, 08 Apr 2023 18:03:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://avaritiachaos.github.io/p/vs-codelive-server%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Live Server：一个具有实时加载功能的小型服务器，可以使用它来html/css/javascript，但是不能用于部署最终站点。也就是说我们可以在项目中实时用live-server作为一个实时服务器实时查看开发的网页或项目效果&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h1 id="vs-使用live-server-时提示open-a-folder-or-workspace-file---open-folder"&gt;vs 使用live server 时提示Open a folder or workspace&amp;hellip; (File -&amp;gt; Open Folder)&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;!-- more --&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如图标题所示，vs在安装live server之后，创建了html文件之后不能打开&lt;br&gt;
Open a folder or workspace… (File -&amp;gt; Open Folder)&lt;br&gt;
解决方案是如下&lt;br&gt;
（注意在此之前已正确安装live server,及修改默认浏览器）&lt;br&gt;
首先关闭vs开发工具再打开&lt;br&gt;
然后 点击file →Open Folder 注意是Folder不是File&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class="cg-figure"&gt;
&lt;div class="cg-wrapper"&gt;
&lt;img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/avaritiachaos/shark-img/lqip/image-20230408181443345.webp"
