&lt;/picture&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;image-20230408181443345&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;h1 id="vscode配置live-server不生效"&gt;vscode配置live server不生效&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;弹出提示 Live Reload is not possible without a head or body tag.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;说明代码里没有body标签。添加完&lt;body&gt;&lt;/body&gt; 保存&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;重新运行open with live server就好了。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>java换jdk版本环境变量配置后不生效解决方法</title><link>https://avaritiachaos.github.io/p/java%E6%8D%A2jdk%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</link><pubDate>Sat, 07 May 2022 11:33:21 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://avaritiachaos.github.io/p/java%E6%8D%A2jdk%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;把系统变量中path的C:\Program Files (x86)\Common Files\Oracle\Java\javapath删除即可&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>